quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,The multiplication distracted/diverted you
  102,2,Until you visited the cemeteries/burial places
  102,3,No but you will/shall know
  102,4,Then no but you will/shall know
  102,5,No but if you know knowledge (of) the assurance/certainty
  102,6,You would see/understand (E) the Hell
  102,7,Then you will see/understand it (with) the assurance`s/certainty`s eye (visually)
  102,8,Then (on) that day you will be asked/questioned (E) about the blessing/goodness